	<h1 class="title">你知道张小涛吗，他可能是中国最厉害的动画师之一</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Jane Perlez</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-05 14:55:02 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/20236/medium/20236.jpg?1451917019" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


